1. HTML Structure

This template offers you to display your events in differnt unique styles. To use this just add the line of code below.


Home Page

Header

This theme is a flexible layout with up to six columns. All of the information within the header area is nested within a div with a class of "header".

2. CSS Files

Template imports number of CSS files.

Custom

Folder: assets\css - 17 css for doing the animation, effects, functionality, etc.

  • bootstrap.css - a used css used for grid on the pages
  • bootstrap-theme.css - a used css used for theme on the pages
  • bootstrap-datepicker.css - a custom css used for datepicker on page
  • bootstrap-slider.css - a custom css used for Range Slider
  • iconmoon.css - a custom css used in all pages for the icons
  • animate.css a custom css used for animation of the all pages
  • chosen.css a custom css used for Fancy Select view
  • swiper.css - a cutsom css used for Image Slider
  • woocommerce.css - a custom css used for woocommerce Pages
  • prettyPhoto.css - a custom css used for Image Light box View
  • daterangepicker.css - a custom css used for Range Date picker
  • jquery.mCustomScrollbar.css - a custom css used for scroll
  • style.css - a custom css used for all Pages Elements...
  • cs-foodbakery-plugin.css - a custom css used for Listings, Search, Filters etc...
  • color.css - a custom css used for Theme Colors
  • widget.css - a custom css used for Theme Widget
  • responsive.css - a custom css used for Other Mobile Devices
  • rtl.css - a custom css used for Other Language

3. Javascript

Template imports number of Javascript files.

Custom

Folder: assets\js - 21 scripts for doing the animation, effects, functionality, etc.

  • jquery.min.js - a used script used for Runing all Custom Functions on pages
  • modernizr.js - a custom script used for html5 tags support
  • bootstrap.js - a used script used for time picker on the pages
  • responsive.menu.js - a custom script used for mobile menu
  • swiper.min.js - a custom script used for slider
  • bootstrap-datepicker.js - a custom script used for datepicker on page
  • chosen.js - a custom script used for Select
  • counter.js - a custom script used for couter
  • filters.js - a custom script used for filters
  • jquery.fitvids.js - a custom script used for Video fit to holder
  • jquery.growl.js - a custom script used for Notification Alert
  • jquery.matchHeight-min.js - a custom script used for Equal Height Elements
  • masonry.js a custom script used for masonry views
  • skills-progress.js - a custom script used for progress
  • bootstrap-slider.js - a custom script used for Range Slider
  • wow.js - a custom script used for Animation
  • jquery.mCustomScrollbar.concat.min.js - a custom script used for scroll
  • daterangepicker.js - a custom script used for Date Range pick
  • functions-plugin.js - a custom script used in Plugin pages for the header, sidebar menu, etc.
  • functions.js - a custom script used in all pages for the header, sidebar menu, etc.
  • jquery.countdown.js - a custom script used for coutdown
